\begin_inset Formula $r$
\end_inset 

 and any 
\begin_inset Formula $\epsilon>0$
\end_inset 

.
 In the above, it was required that 
\begin_inset Formula $r<2$
\end_inset 

, but other 
\begin_inset Formula $r$
\end_inset 

's are easily accomadated.
 Simply changing the definition to
