\begin_inset Formula \[
d_{n}=\sum_{k=n_{0}}^{n}(-1)^{k}\left({n\atop k}\right)\, f(k)\]

\end_inset 

 allows for any 
\begin_inset Formula $r<n_{0}$
\end_inset 

.
